            <div class="nav-container">
                <button class="btn btn-prev" onclick="changePage(-1)">❮ Kembali</button>
                <button class="btn" onclick="changePage(1)">Lanjut ❯</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- HALAMAN 3 -->
        <div class="page" id="p3">
            <!-- Dekor Pinggir Halaman 3 -->
            <div class="deco-flower fl-top-left"><div class="flower-core"></div></div>
            <div class="deco-flower fl-top-right"><div class="flower-core"></div></div>
            <div class="deco-flower fl-bot-left"><div class="flower-core"></div></div>
            <div class="deco-star st2">✨</div>
            <div class="deco-star st3">✨</div>

            <!-- Nailong Full Body -->
            <div class="nailong-fullbody" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
                <div class="nailong-avatar" style="margin-bottom:0; z-index:4;">
                    <div class="nailong-horn"></div>
                    <div class="nailong-eyes left"></div>
                    <div class="nailong-eyes right"></div>
                    <div class="nailong-mouth" style="height:14px; border-radius:50%;"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="nailong-body"><div class="nailong-belly"></div></div>
                <div class="nailong-hand left"></div>
                <div class="nailong-hand right"></div>
                <div class="nailong-foot left"></div>
                <div class="nailong-foot right"></div>
                <div class="nailong-tail"></div>
            </div>

            <h1>Selamat <span>Ulang Tahun!</span></h1>
            <p><b>Suji Pranandito🎂🤍</b></p>
            <p>"Di hari lahirmu ini, dia tidak ingin meminta banyak pada semesta, selain meminta agar tawa tangguhmu itu tidak pernah pudar. Terima kasih ya sudah tumbuh menjadi jiwa yang sekuat dan seindah ini."</p>
            
            <div class="nav-container">
